reviewText: good alternative review on where is the money going and why
Great documentary about the industry and all the smoke and mirrors amongst celebrities.

The movie explains what happens when the checks stop coming in. Everyone has a false expectation of what it is like to become a celebrity and not understand that with more money comes more responsibility. Buying more things don't keep you rich. I wish the documentary went more into how to invest and grow your money and not just save.
Nice dvd!! Limited info but I wish there was more information it was not worth what I paid

This is a documentary about rich African-Americans who go broke when the paycheck stops. The film looks at music, film, NFL, and NBA.  It goes into the details of just a few lives and glosses over the rest with headlines. It looks at some on the whys and hows and still had a hard time filling up 51 minutes.
Excellent!  Very Powerful Information!  A Must See !
Very good movie. It really made me think about what goes on in the entertainment industry.
